fullName.value: WD repeat and HMG-box DNA-binding protein 1

texts.value: Core replisome component that acts as a replication initiation factor. Binds directly to the CMG complex and functions as a hub to recruit additional proteins to the replication fork

Trimer (PubMed:32453425, PubMed:34694004). Interacts with the polymerase alpha catalytic subunit POLA1. Interacts with MCM10 (PubMed:17761813). Interacts with DNA2 (PubMed:22570476). Interacts with CDC45 and GINS2 subunit of GINS complex; these interactions associate WDHD1 with the CMG helicase complex (PubMed:32453425, PubMed:34694004)
